title: AskFest
body:
Funny you should ask that, #line:10000400
There actually is a new festival coming soon. #line:10000500
The Fey Masquerade! #line:10000600
However it may not be here for a couple years. #line:10000700
If you're looking for something to do, talk to Riah. #line:10000800
She recently requested a permit from me for her own festival. #line:10000900
However, I denied her because she had no direction for the event. #line:10001000
[[End]]
